     <p><strong><a name="Downing_S" id="Downing_S"></a>Downing Street Foundation Women's Scholarship</strong></p> 
     <p>The Downing Street Foundation Women's Scholarship was established by the Downing Street Foundation in the late 1980s to encourage and support female leadership at Westmont College. Preference is given to students whose home state is Colorado and who are involved in Young Life.</p> 
