     <p><strong><a name="W_M_Fochler" id="W_M_Fochler"></a>William and Marcia Fochler Endowed Scholarship</strong></p> 
     <p>In 1979, William Fochler was the chair of the Parents’ Campaign in the first major fund drive at Westmont. William and Marcia believed in a liberal arts education, and especially in an education that values Christian beliefs. Since 1997, this scholarship has been awarded to financially deserving students.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </p> 
