     <p><img src="http://westmont.edu/giving/images/GoehnerBev2.JPG" width="209" height="227" alt="Bev Goehner"></p> 
     <p>Family and friends established the Bev Goehner Memorial Scholarship Endowment in her honor. She was a woman of deep faith who exhibited the fragrance of Christ to all those around her. Bev was a vibrant, loving, beautiful woman, who deeply loved her Lord and served Him all the days of her life. She was a friend of the college, a proud Westmont parent, and committed to the college’s mission. This scholarship is awarded to financially deserving students who will be involved in elementary education and is also based on academic merit.<br> </p> 
