     <p><strong><a name="Lundberg" id="Lundberg"></a>Lundberg Men's Endowed Scholarship</strong></p> 
     <p>Cliff and Diane Lundberg established the Lundberg Men's Endowed Scholarship. Cliff ’65 and Diane ’66 are both graduates of Westmont College. In 1965, Cliff was captain of Westmont’s first men’s soccer team. He served on the Westmont College Board of Trustees from 1993-2002 and has been an employee of the advancement office. They are faithful supporters, donors, and volunteers of the college. This scholarship is awarded to male varsity soccer athletes.&nbsp; For more information on Cliff click <a href="http://blogs.westmont.edu/magazine/1998/02/02/leading-by-example/">here</a>.&nbsp; </p> 
