     <p>This scholarship was established in memory of Roger R. Post. Roger was a part of Westmont for 20 years, serving on the Board of Trustees. Board of Trustee members fondly remember him for initiating and leading the prayer and share time during Trustee worship. Roger Post was a man of deep faith and was dedicated to reaching teenagers for Jesus Christ. This scholarship is therefore awarded to students who have demonstrated leadership ability in a Young Life program or youth ministry before attending Westmont. This scholarship was first awarded in 2007.</p> 
